{"tid":640234,"cid":31,"subCid":7,"title":"[改詞][入嚟放低你家主子J圖]《只想待你身邊》[原曲：陳奕迅-我們]","createTime":"2018-04-24T06:52:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-15T02:53:11.000Z","uid":108844,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"a0c21b98441f08f2a56d365e705be4d07711d90b","tid":640234,"uid":108844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T06:52:47.000Z","msg":"原曲：<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/dhjomo8W6Lc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fdhjomo8W6Lc&d=dwnxjq7AAAmXthCMTWeEytibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=e7a1ccd2\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/dhjomo8W6Lc</a><br />\n<br />\n-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n話說細佬係三隻貓嘅奴才<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其中大女由出世到我帶佢入屋之前嘅三個月都一直流浪街頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所以佢好怕生保，但神奇嘅係由佢第一日入屋開始就非常痴我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 第二晚就已經同我一齊訓，直到依家都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n平時我喺屋企佢一定會跟住我，仲會成日喵喵叫同我講嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 因為咁我覺得我地好似知道對方諗緊咩咁<br />\n甚至前排失戀，佢都會特別陪住我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 令我有啲懷疑佢係人扮嘅<br />\n所以哩首歌決定用佢嘅角度FF<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n《只想待你身邊》<br />\n<br />\n心傷掉 不緊要<br />\n尚有人願照料<br />\n不可怕 再多的傷疤<br />\n仍然樂於蹦跳 吃睡叫囂<br />\n<br />\n怎麼淚 滴濕眼<br />\n無聊地仰望 長夜漫漫<br />\n不想打斷 情願坐好在旁<br />\n人類若不善忘 更淒愴<br />\n<br />\n只想待你身邊 即使心情太壞 在失眠<br />\n看你懊惱的書寫數篇<br />\n我最多促膝半天<br />\n陪伴你對著誰在掛牽<br />\n只想待你身邊 無論天色轉變<br />\n俗世得你珍惜我 帶我走出過錯<br />\n<br />\n少她在 未必慣<br />\n從前若見面 無窮爛漫<br />\n灰心的你 仍然未肯淡忘<br />\n人類若果善忘 更開朗<br />\n<br />\n只想待你身邊 即使心情太壞 在失眠<br />\n看你懊惱的書寫數篇<br />\n我最多促膝半天<br />\n陪伴你對著誰在掛牽<br />\n只想待你身邊 無論天色轉變<br />\n俗世得你珍惜我 帶我走出過錯<br />\n<br />\n知足便 有福了<br />\n遇見原是美妙<br />\n依偎你臂彎安躺半宵<br />\n願會安撫你心境 渺渺"},{"pid":"cf36953cc9d258d4799c328328c6662eb1818b7c","tid":640234,"uid":108844,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T06:55:04.000Z","msg":"死女包個pose又同Eason個mv封面幾似<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec66e6b1561ef10581b52bce9fa30dcc000a49b7","tid":640234,"uid":40429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T07:30:04.000Z","msg":"人類若果善忘 更開朗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2297edb213d97c4e635da24d25da3eddaaceb5b4","tid":640234,"uid":108844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ec66e6b1561ef10581b52bce9fa30dcc000a49b7","tid":640234,"uid":40429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T07:30:04.000Z","msg":"人類若果善忘 更開朗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T08:20:46.000Z","msg":"可惜記性太好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54fa9d865ff0aa18dad918b6bace5eb192871f10","tid":640234,"uid":62717,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T10:07:32.000Z","msg":"唔太啱音喎...或者你唱一次出黎聽聽先？"},{"pid":"07b6003fbd17f3ca5c527f84c306678e8d139c88","tid":640234,"uid":108844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"54fa9d865ff0aa18dad918b6bace5eb192871f10","tid":640234,"uid":62717,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T10:07:32.000Z","msg":"唔太啱音喎...或者你唱一次出黎聽聽先？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T10:27:08.000Z","msg":"係咪仍然未肯淡忘嗰句<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 原來我聽錯咗做do re me<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真正唱係do me me<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其他check過應該冇問題<im